WEBVTT

00:00:04.139 --> 00:00:32.009
Peace, security, your balance, finding support.

00:00:32.009 --> 00:00:39.219
Jehovah promised, grasping your right hand, saying to you,

00:00:39.219 --> 00:00:43.219
Do not be afraid, I will help you.

00:00:43.219 --> 00:00:52.219
He stretches out his hand to us every day through magazines, books, films, videos.

00:00:52.219 --> 00:00:56.219
They help us to live by his word.

00:00:56.219 --> 00:01:03.219
All this is available to us thanks to the cooperation of 90 branch offices throughout the world.

00:01:03.219 --> 00:01:08.219
One of them is in Celtus.

00:01:08.219 --> 00:01:15.219
Over 30 persons translate the articles and videos from English into German.

00:01:15.219 --> 00:01:26.129
They are recorded and published on our website or are prepared for print.

00:01:26.129 --> 00:01:40.680
Large editions are produced at high speed. Advanced technology is used.

00:01:40.680 --> 00:02:17.680
The entire process focuses on quality.

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:51.939
Literature for 1.3 million brothers is sent from here in 300 languages.

00:02:51.939 --> 00:02:56.939
Literature is packed for over 16,500 congregations.

00:02:56.939 --> 00:03:09.419
It is sent to all four corners of the earth.

00:03:09.419 --> 00:03:21.259
Even to the most eastern parts of Asia, a branch committee coordinates all Bethel operations.

00:03:21.259 --> 00:03:31.009
These experienced men also look after the preaching work throughout the branch territory.

00:03:31.009 --> 00:03:43.979
Conventions are organised. The activity of circuit overseers is coordinated.

00:03:43.979 --> 00:03:49.129
Schools are also planned.

00:03:49.129 --> 00:03:56.129
The idea behind these schools is for the graduates to lend a helping hand to the congregations.

00:03:56.129 --> 00:04:10.900
We loved the school. It was a special training from Jehovah.

00:04:10.900 --> 00:04:23.740
Concepts are developed and executed for the construction, extension and renovation of Bethel homes and assembly halls.

00:04:23.740 --> 00:04:32.420
When we found the lightning, when we were assigned to do an assembly hall, we first looked for properties.

00:04:32.420 --> 00:04:37.420
It has to be large enough and were located for the brothers to easily reach.

00:04:37.420 --> 00:04:42.420
We also look for sufficient parking space and good public transport.

00:04:42.420 --> 00:04:46.420
We usually have several properties to choose from.

00:04:46.420 --> 00:04:49.420
Then we work out different options and drawings for each side.

00:04:49.420 --> 00:04:54.420
After that, we send these options to the governing body for review and approval.

00:04:54.420 --> 00:05:04.470
For questions on non-blood medical management,

00:05:04.470 --> 00:05:09.470
600 brothers in 80 hospital liaison committees are available.

00:05:09.470 --> 00:05:15.470
The commitment of the brothers in the hospital liaison committees has always been amazing to me.

00:05:15.470 --> 00:05:20.470
Everything they do for their brothers is out of love and without payment.

00:05:20.470 --> 00:05:31.310
When we think of such a service, we clearly see Jehovah's Hand.

00:05:31.310 --> 00:05:44.730
At Bethel, all live together like a big family.

00:05:44.730 --> 00:05:52.730
Of course, the spiritual program is very important.

00:05:52.730 --> 00:05:57.730
We enjoy the well-prepared comments that morning worship.

00:05:57.730 --> 00:06:02.730
And then, of course, we look forward to watch our study on Monday evening,

00:06:02.730 --> 00:06:13.209
when the Bethel family comes together to study God's words of study.

00:06:13.209 --> 00:06:18.209
All the work accomplished here is not just any kind of work.

00:06:18.209 --> 00:06:31.160
False loving devotion.

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:47.819
It is sacred service, no matter where one comes from.

00:06:47.819 --> 00:06:57.850
No matter what the assignment, the common goal is

00:06:57.850 --> 00:07:09.790
to promote the worldwide work to honor Jehovah.

00:07:09.790 --> 00:07:26.660
Jehovah helps us to remain strong in the faith,

00:07:26.660 --> 00:07:37.339
to reach out for his hand toward a bright future.
